    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 <strong>Age of Enchantment</strong>，这是一款融合了塔防、卡组构筑与 D&amp;D 的游戏，正是你一直期待的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >塔防 + 卡组构筑 + D&amp;D</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神器系统</strong>：通过升级或在游戏中发现神器，并使用精华购买来解锁神器。随后，你可以在出战配置中设置它们，以最大化你的构筑并寻找最强大的协同效果。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>职业主题防御塔</strong>：你的防御塔以 D&amp;D 职业为原型。以战士与法师开局，并随着等级提升解锁圣骑士、牧师、野蛮人和术士。每座防御塔拥有 3 条不同的升级路线，每条路线包含 3 个阶级。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/d3b19738d0ce1fc498091b9844b1e685.poster.avif?t=1771858064\" width=1170 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/d3b19738d0ce1fc498091b9844b1e685.webm?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/d3b19738d0ce1fc498091b9844b1e685.mp4?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战士</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >法师</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >牧师</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >圣骑士</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >术士</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >野蛮人</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/9589ac6f4bdcd71d6c9daa7020c4e7d8.poster.avif?t=1771858064\" width=1170 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/9589ac6f4bdcd71d6c9daa7020c4e7d8.webm?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/9589ac6f4bdcd71d6c9daa7020c4e7d8.mp4?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在每张地图前选择你的出战配置以定制你的策略</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设置你的防御塔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的神器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过疯狂之颅调整难度——并获得巨额奖励。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/7b0fcba42fdcd73de499a96b3d045abb.poster.avif?t=1771858064\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/7b0fcba42fdcd73de499a96b3d045abb.webm?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/7b0fcba42fdcd73de499a96b3d045abb.mp4?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >卡组构筑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向 RNG 之神祈祷，通过献祭卡牌来获得最适合你构筑的卡牌，或使用献祭系统移除你不需要的卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/770ca05354ad0af7e82ec34d6590a2d4.poster.avif?t=1771858064\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/770ca05354ad0af7e82ec34d6590a2d4.webm?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/770ca05354ad0af7e82ec34d6590a2d4.mp4?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无限组合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 10 张不同的地图中战斗，运用你的防御塔、附魔、法术与神器取得胜利。拥有超过 50 件神器、100 多张卡牌以及总计 18 个防御塔阶级，你能发现哪些协同效果？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/0e25c608919aeb27ce4f32989b3f3145.poster.avif?t=1771858064\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/0e25c608919aeb27ce4f32989b3f3145.webm?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046020/extras/0e25c608919aeb27ce4f32989b3f3145.mp4?t=1771858064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
